<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<!DOCTYPE task PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Task//EN" "task.dtd" []>
<task xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="specifying-indent-size-of-blocks" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:task.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Specifying Indent Size of Blocks</title>
  <taskbody id="body">
    <context>
      <p>When you switch to the Markup Mode, markup tags are displayed. Nested elements are indented as blocks. The default indentation of blocks can be changed. </p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step>
        <cmd>Call up the <keyword>Preferences Dialog</keyword>.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>To call up the <keyword>Preferences Dialog</keyword>, choose <menucascade>
              <uicontrol>Tools</uicontrol>
              <uicontrol>Preferences</uicontrol>
            </menucascade>.</p>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Select the <keyword>Tag Style tab</keyword>.</cmd>
        <info>
          <fig>
            <title>Tag Style tab.</title>
            <image href="preferences-dialog-tag-style-tab-block-indent.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
          </fig>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>To change the indent size of blocks, specify the value in the <uicontrol>Block indent</uicontrol> field.</cmd>
        <info>
          <note>
            <p>The higher the value, the bigger the indent size of blocks. The default value is 10.</p>
            <fig>
              <title>Block indent sizes 10 and 30 compared.</title>
              <image href="block-indents-compared.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
            </fig>
          </note>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Apply</uicontrol> button to apply the settings.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Close</uicontrol> button to close the dialog.</cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
</task>
